channel.title: What should I make a website on?
channel.description: I just want to make a website to practice but I really don't know anything to make a website about so any ideas would be great. But please refrain from anything that has to do with shit or sex or any other crap!

item.title: What should I make a website on?
item.dc:creator: @Server-Unknown.Net Server-Unknown.Net
item.description:
@Server-Unknown.Net wrote:

Well best way you should practice is drawing template skeletons on a sheet of paper like I do. That should help you get familiar with layout designing so you don’t have a hard time thinking. Especially when you know the skeletal of over 40 templates.
